text: Dear @UPSHelp. I was due to get a delivery today though with no time slot. I waited in all day and nothing came. No delivery, no info, no contact. And if I reschedule online I can’t request a time just another whole day. Absolutely terrible service.

We live in a modern world of mobiles, tracking & laptops. But for @UPS it’s still 1983 so I had to wait in all day for a delivery that never came. And now they can’t say where my parcel is or when it will arrive. Useless.
